Subject: [PATCH v6 06/11] arm64: dts: ti: k3-am62a7-sk: Enable IPC with remote processors
Date: Fri, 4 Apr 2025 19:15:13 -0500
Message-ID: <20250405001518.1315273-7-jm@ti.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.49.0
